## Archon Proverb
> All must aspire to the Perfection of Eledon!
> In Shirayla we find redemption and order;
> In Logos we find temperance and pure astra;
> In Xalia we find purity and justice;
> In Delaran we find divine wrath and the purging of unbelief;
> In Korryn we find celerity and precision;
> In Borial we find strength and steadfastness;
> In Eledon, all these are Perfected: for this we must Hunger!
